title: Transcend launches 1TB JetDrive flush SD card designed for the new MacBook Pro
content:
After launching its JetDrive Lite 330 expansion cards earlier this year, Transcend is out today with a new made specifically for the latest MacBook Pro. With a clean design that sits fully flush with your notebook, the 1TB JetDrive makes it seamless to expand your MacBook Pro’s storage.

more…

The post Transcend launches 1TB JetDrive flush SD card designed for the new MacBook Pro appeared first on 9to5Mac.
description: Transcend has launched its largest capacity yet of its JetDrive Lite 330. The new flush SD card for MacBook Pro offers 1TB of storage.
